name: Classics.
description:
These are the classical girl. The one who shares a love for cardigans, Birkenstock's, and just a "little" spice every once in a while.

These Levi's 505s are distressed just right. They are high-waisted and feature the signature Levi's leather tab on the back hip. 

These shorts are sized 30. Like most Levi's, they run small and fit a 27 almost perfectly.

Be sure to check the NEWS section for DISCOUNT codes!

name: Bad Gyal
description:
Inspired by our favorite Island girl, Rihanna, "Bad Gyal" is a pair of distressed, vintage, Levi shorts, studded to perfection. 

Designed to hug you in all the right places, these Levi red tab, button fly shorts run a little smaller than their size. 

The size is marked as a 30, but will fit a 27 the same way. 

Features same "stair" design on front left pocket and back right pocket. 

These are definitely a favorite.

Be sure to check the NEWS section for discounts!

name: Milky Way
description:
Vintage pair of premium Jordache denim that's been bleached, destroyed and studded. 

Shorts feature the Jordache leather tab on the back right hip, also a studded cross on the back right pocket. Front left panel of the shorts is studded down the front. 

Each pair is one of a kind!

This pair is a size 13/14.

Don't forget to check NEWS for the latest discounts!

name: Custom
description:
Each item is made with love and handled with care.

Custom prices are determined first by type, then through a simple consultation. 

Please visit the contact page and send us an email detailing what you'd like done. Once we're in contact, we can begin discussing specifications to get your custom order EXACTLY how you want it!

Custom pieces require you to mail the item to me, therefore there is NO shipping cost on this item. It will be shipped back to you at no cost. 

PLEASE DO NOT ORDER CUSTOM ITEMS HERE. AN INVOICE WILL BE E-MAILED TO YOU AFTER CONSULTATION.
